Description: The tidyvpc package provides a fast and easy way to perform a Visual Predictive Check (VPC), while accounting for stratification, censoring, and prediction correction. Using piping from magrittr, the intuitive syntax gives users a flexible and powerful method to generate VPCs using both traditional binning and a new binless approach with Additive Quantile Regression (AQR) and LOESS prediction correction.
URL: https://github.com/jameswcraig/tidyvpc
BugReports: https://github.com/jameswcraig/tidyvpc/issues
